text: Faristenia impenicilla is a moth in the family Gelechiidae. It is found in China (Shaanxi)., 1998: A taxonomic review of the genus Faristenia from China (Lepidoptera: Gelechiidae). Acta Zootaxonomica Sinica 23 (4): 386-398. ==References== Category:Faristenia Category:Moths described in 1998
title: Faristenia impenicilla
